contract_type.raw_snippet: b) “Agreement” means this Supply Agreement for the Product, including all Exhibits attached hereto;

notice_period.raw_snippet: a) Customer delivers written notice of termination to Supplier at least [* * *] prior to the expiration date of the Initial Term, which termination shall be effective as of the expiration date of the Initial Term;
notice_period.reasoning: This clause provides the advance notice required to terminate at the end of the Initial Term, thereby preventing the automatic continuation into the Renewal Term. The specific period is redacted, so the exact number of days cannot be normalized.

expiration_date.raw_snippet: This Agreement shall commence on the Effective Date and shall be valid until the [* * *] (the “Initial Term”).
expiration_date.reasoning: This is the primary term/expiration statement. The specific end point is redacted, so no calculable or relative duration can be normalized.

Should the Parties have not agreed to the following agreement by [* * *], this Agreement shall automatically stay in force for a maximum of
